{"tid":1844902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【NBA】高比拜仁坐直升機意外中身亡………","createTime":"2020-01-26T23:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T01:29:03.000Z","uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee12cf77fd1221ccf08efd6800fc12c84d7c3cc4","tid":1844902,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:16:25.000Z","msg":"美國籃球明星高比拜仁在直升機意外中身亡<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒報道，美國NBA籃球明星高比拜仁在直升機意外中身亡，享年41歲。意外在美國星期日發生，報道表示，高比拜仁與另外至少三人，乘坐他的私人直升機，據報期間發生火警，之後墜毀，事件中無人生還。報道表示，高比拜仁的妻子並不在機上。<br />\n<br />\n2020-01-27 03:46:52 (1)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d77d79c846d14c54a97ede879847652f60929e5","tid":1844902,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:17:04.000Z","msg":"wtf"},{"pid":"d4bb0d2dabca85598e82045c0943327b2250fec6","tid":1844902,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:17:51.000Z","msg":"痴線架"},{"pid":"534e78d7131c646ddd8e8dcac0e4932776627e8b","tid":1844902,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4676e14e1390334fa10726613272dd27d6a564","tid":1844902,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:34:15.000Z","msg":"哇個老婆fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e62ca9f222b23309c4245b3f51b7ed149d54f2","tid":1844902,"uid":325200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:50:42.000Z","msg":"陰謀論 佢老婆請殺手殺佢"},{"pid":"43ee977277227a01d99106f01c647f1309898b59","tid":1844902,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T01:29:03.000Z","msg":"佢老婆幾歲"}]}